
- **app.js** – Node.js application code
- **package.json** – Node.js project metadata and dependencies
- **Dockerfile** – Instructions for building the Docker image
- **deployment.yaml** – Kubernetes Deployment configuration with probes, resource limits, and scaling
- **README.md** – Project documentation

---

## ⚙️ Setup & Run Locally

### 1. Clone the repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/lutherdpage/DevOps-Demo-App-Kubernetes-Deployment.git
cd DevOps-Demo-App-Kubernetes-Deployment

docker build -t devops-demo-app .

docker images

minikube image load devops-demo-app

kubectl apply -f deployment.yaml
kubectl expose deployment devops-demo-deployment --type=NodePort --port=3000

kubectl get pods -o wide
kubectl get services

minikube service devops-demo-deployment --url

kubectl scale deployment devops-demo-deployment --replicas=<number_of_replicas>
kubectl get pods -o wide

